        <bt:String id="Tip0" DefaultValue="Open Rostrum&apos;s general settings — including how Rostrum loads on every document and how to turn that off." />
        <bt:String id="Tip1" DefaultValue="Hide all non-keeper body text (cards), keeping headings, cites, analytics, and highlighted runs. Run it again after editing to hide newly typed or pasted text." />
        <bt:String id="Tip2" DefaultValue="Reveal everything Rostrum hid. Convergent — safe to run from any state." />
        <bt:String id="Tip3" DefaultValue="Apply Rostrum heading/cite sizes and the pocket box, and repair mis-styled cites. Reflows the document; needs desktop Word 1.5+." />
